data.description: This exceptional property is more than a house; it's an embodiment of refined living in Covington, Georgia. From its impeccable design to its idyllic surroundings, this is a place where cherished memories are created and where dreams are realized. The expansive master bedroom is a serene oasis, featuring a generous sitting area, perfect for quiet moments of relaxation. The master bathroom features a soaking tub, walk-in shower, and his-and-hers vanities that lead to a large walk-in closet, providing ample space to organize and showcase your wardrobe. The renovated eat-in kitchen is a contemporary masterpiece, adorned with gleaming stainless steel appliances and a central island that doubles as a stylish breakfast bar. It seamlessly opens up to the spacious living area, bathed in natural light, offering an inviting and connected space for both culinary delights and relaxed family gatherings. This home is new and everything is less than a year old. Come out and see your forever home.
